ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of NORMAN BETTS of Fredericton, New Brunswick, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending February 28, 2017, in the place of Richard McGaw, effective July 2, 2014.
